import React,{useState,useEffect} from 'react'; import {Table} from 'react-bootstrap'; function Summary(props) { return (
Profit/Loss {props.summary.pnl}
NPV {props.summary.npv}
Cash Deposited {props.summary.accountbalance}
Margin Used {props.summary.marginused}
Margin(%) {props.summary.marginlevel}
Margin Free {props.summary.marginfree}
); } export default Summary;
